snippet.title: Best VGM 737 - Chip 'n Dale : Rescue Rangers - Happy Cat Factory (Stage J)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Chip 'n Dale: Rescue Rangers (1990)
Happy Cat Factory (Stage J)
Soshihiro Sakaguchi
